I am happy with my Newsfeed the way it is ! It comes and goes. But I'm not happy with my Timeline anymore because I used to keep things that I love but    
They started disappearing from there sometime ago, mainly the ones I love the most, like Elvis Presley's photos, and my beautiful Tigers photos, lovely views. I don't erased them ! Where are they ?!! I want them back !My Timeline is for my appreciation and my friends !!Please tell me or teach me what to do to have them back !!!   Thanks

replies.message: Hey Marise. If your posts are disappearing and then reappearing on your Timeline, let us know: https://www.facebook.com/help/186570224871049 -Hailey
